{"tid":810322,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 我老豆買華仔演唱會，俾我鬧到喊","createTime":"2018-09-08T01:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T08:56:43.000Z","uid":123335,"like":19,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"88aeeaf0c3ef814d6716580c9e341b5dea8c50fe","tid":810322,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:33:35.000Z","msg":"我係華仔fans 黎<br />\n<br />\n本身同老豆約好話幫我買華仔演唱會。<br />\n老豆話：「呀仔，你安心返工啦，我幫你排隊買飛啦」<br />\n點知收工返黎後<br />\n發覺老豆買撚錯左<br />\n琴晚食晚餐果陣咪鬧佢囉：「屌你on9架？華仔演唱會飛你都買錯？ 」<br />\n嘈到幾混亂下，就順手拎起飯檯上既油炸鬼<br />\n猛咁拍打自己出氣，喊住咁拍打：「老豆呀，你唔識買就唔好逞英雄去買，你而家買錯咗，點收科啊？」<br />\n好彩呀媽即刻出黎阻止我，做和事佬<br />\n唔洗搞到報警<br />\n<br />\n但依我再諗返成件事<br />\n我老豆真係抵鬧嘅：「一諗起佢買左咩演唱會飛，就慶過火屎。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/092930_f6d2e47f35ec6350b635ee452b10b8d6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F092930_f6d2e47f35ec6350b635ee452b10b8d6.jpeg&h=5d15c5ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb50816c501805559a7c067e7d8f0c7fb51f061","tid":810322,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"ching 好波"},{"pid":"f5dde4fd479b4ead80d6fa1f2f09a71ab8048e57","tid":810322,"uid":51594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:58:09.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"20c6434c66cbfe78bdaa6416fc204f2cc51b6643","tid":810322,"uid":143221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a86379e595cf2affca631a6fce2cabaf9081ec2","tid":810322,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3338dd22018fcba2949b8e440b766950d6a90845","tid":810322,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"不孝子